---
title: Writings By JDRanpariya
layout: layouts/base
section: "writings index"
---

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 flex flex-col gap-16">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">Writings</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Thoughts, experiments, and explorations across AI, neuroscience, bio, and embodied intelligence. 
      These are my reflections and in-depth posts on what I'm exploring.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- List of posts -->
  <div class="space-y-12">
    {% for post in collections.writings %}
      <article class="space-y-2 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2 text-primary text-accent capitalize">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</section>

